text: Schwaigen is a municipality in the district of Garmisch-Partenkirchen in Upper Bavaria in Germany. == Districts == Schwaigen has six districts: * Apfelbichel * Fuchsloch * Grafenaschau * Hinterbraunau * Plaicken * Vorderbraunau == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Garmisch- Partenkirchen (district)
